unspecified banks to combat tax evasion and money laundering,
 Hospodarske Noviny  reported, citing a Finance Ministry official.  The checks will focus mainly on smaller banks with private
clientele that report few suspicious financial transactions, the
newspaper said, citing Milan Cicer, head of the Finance
